 Verification

 1. uv run pytest — Python tests still pass
 2. deno task test — Deno tests still pass
 3. Push to a branch, open a PR — verify the test job runs green on GitHub
 4. Merge to master — verify deploy job triggers (will fail until droplet is set up + secrets added, which is expected)
